{
  "skyrimnet_knowledge_pack": {
    "author": "_gaius",
    "description": "Windhelm's notable people — Ulfric Stormcloak's court, the Gray Quarter Dunmer, the Shatter-Shield clan in their grief, and the boy performing the Black Sacrament in his abandoned house.",
    "entry_count": 66,
    "exported_at": "2026-05-18T05:00:00Z",
    "format_version": 2,
    "name": "_VKP - Notable People In Windhelm",
    "npc_groups": [],
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "entries": [
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Ulfric Stormcloak is the Jarl of Windhelm and leader of the Stormcloak rebellion against the Empire. Voice-trained at High Hrothgar, killed High King Torygg in single combat, and now wages war for an independent Skyrim.",
        "display_name": "Ulfric Stormcloak - Jarl of Windhelm",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.95,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.ulfric",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Ulfric Stormcloak",
          "Jarl",
          "Windhelm",
          "Stormcloak",
          "High King",
          "Markarth",
          "Thalmor",
          "rebellion",
          "military",
          "leadership"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"@CWSonsFaction\")",
        "content": "Galmar Stone-Fist commands the Stormcloak military under Ulfric. Hard old Nord, scarred, the kind of war-chief who runs his sons through their drills before dawn.",
        "display_name": "Galmar Stone-Fist - Ulfric's Second",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.9,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.galmar",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Galmar Stone-Fist",
          "Stormcloak",
          "Windhelm",
          "Palace of the Kings",
          "Ulfric",
          "military",
          "soldier",
          "rebellion"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Jorleif is Ulfric's steward at the Palace of the Kings. Older Nord, practical, handles the city's daily business while Ulfric handles the rebellion.",
        "display_name": "Jorleif - Steward",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.75,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.jorleif",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Jorleif",
          "steward",
          "Windhelm",
          "Ulfric",
          "Palace of the Kings",
          "governance",
          "administration",
          "stewardship"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Wuunferth the Unliving is Ulfric's court mage — old, reclusive, suspected of necromancy by half of Windhelm including the Stormcloak guards he answers to. He has been investigating the Butcher killings privately.",
        "display_name": "Wuunferth the Unliving - Court Mage",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.85,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.wuunferth",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Wuunferth the Unliving",
          "court mage",
          "Windhelm",
          "Ulfric",
          "Necromancer's Amulet",
          "magic",
          "investigation",
          "necromancy",
          "mystery"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"@CWSonsFaction\")",
        "content": "Yrsarald Thrice-Pierced is one of Ulfric's senior Stormcloak officers — the man named for the three arrows he survived at the Battle of Markarth. Drinks at the Palace tables when he isn't in the field.",
        "display_name": "Yrsarald Thrice-Pierced - Stormcloak Officer",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.7,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.yrsarald",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Yrsarald Thrice-Pierced",
          "Stormcloak",
          "Windhelm",
          "officer",
          "Palace of the Kings",
          "military",
          "soldier",
          "rebellion"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Brunwulf Free-Winter is the Imperial-aligned Nord who would replace Ulfric as Jarl of Eastmarch. Unusually for a Nord of Windhelm, he openly defends the Dunmer of the Gray Quarter against their tormentors.",
        "display_name": "Brunwulf Free-Winter - Imperial Alternative",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.8,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.brunwulf",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Brunwulf Free-Winter",
          "Windhelm",
          "Imperial",
          "alternative Jarl",
          "Dunmer ally",
          "nobility",
          "leadership",
          "discrimination"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Rolff Stone-Fist is Galmar's drunk younger brother. Picks fights with the Dunmer of the Gray Quarter most nights — Galmar covers for him because they share blood, but barely.",
        "display_name": "Rolff Stone-Fist - Drunken Brother",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.6,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.rolff",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Rolff Stone-Fist",
          "Windhelm",
          "Galmar",
          "drunk",
          "racist",
          "Gray Quarter",
          "discrimination",
          "violence",
          "tavern"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Elda Early-Dawn runs Candlehearth Hall in Windhelm's Stone Quarter. The death of her server Susanna the Wicked has shaken her — she's been short-handed since.",
        "display_name": "Elda Early-Dawn - Candlehearth Hall",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.7,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.elda",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Elda Early-Dawn",
          "Candlehearth Hall",
          "Windhelm",
          "innkeeper",
          "Susanna",
          "hospitality",
          "grief",
          "tavern"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Tova Shatter-Shield grieves for her daughter Friga, killed by the Butcher of Windhelm. Her surviving daughter Nilsine bears the weight of her mother's grief in silence.",
        "display_name": "Tova Shatter-Shield - Grieving Mother",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.75,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.tova",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Tova Shatter-Shield",
          "Windhelm",
          "Friga",
          "Nilsine",
          "grief",
          "clan",
          "mother",
          "murder",
          "family"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Torbjorn Shatter-Shield runs the family shipping out of Windhelm's docks. Stoic Nord patriarch, mourning his daughter Friga and watching his wife crumble.",
        "display_name": "Torbjorn Shatter-Shield - Grieving Father",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.7,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.torbjorn",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Torbjorn Shatter-Shield",
