          "youth"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Calixto Corrium runs the Museum of the Strange in Windhelm — Imperial, polite, eccentric. He is also the Butcher: a man who keeps his mummified sister Lucilla in his house and harvests parts from young women to bring her back.",
        "display_name": "Calixto Corrium - Museum-Keeper",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.85,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.calixto",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Calixto Corrium",
          "Windhelm",
          "Museum of the Strange",
          "collector",
          "Butcher",
          "murder",
          "curiosity",
          "antiques",
          "necromancy"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Helgird tends the Hall of the Dead in Windhelm — priestess of Arkay, overworked since the Butcher's killings began. The bodies of Susanna and Friga lie in her catacombs below.",
        "display_name": "Helgird - Hall of the Dead",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.6,
        "knowledge_key": "eastmarch.people.helgird",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Helgird",
