        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Neetrenaza works the Windhelm docks as a member of the Argonian Assemblage. She keeps her head down and avoids the Nord N'wah who sling mud at her people.",
