        "content": "Scouts-Many-Marshes is an Argonian dockworker living in the isolated Argonian Assemblage in Windhelm. He works the docks alongside his fellow Saxhleel.",
        "display_name": "Scouts-Many-Marshes - Dockworker",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.5,
