        "content": "Shahvee is an Argonian dockworker in Windhelm, known for her unusually cheerful disposition despite living in the squalid Argonian Assemblage. She believes hard work and a positive outlook will see her through.",
        "display_name": "Shahvee - Dockworker",
        "emotion": "",
