        "content": "Stands-In-Shallows is an Argonian dockworker living in the Assemblage outside Windhelm's walls. He keeps to himself and works the loading cranes at the docks.",
        "display_name": "Stands-In-Shallows - Dockworker",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.5,
