        "content": "Aval Atheron lives in the Gray Quarter with his siblings Faryl and Suvaris. Dunmer, young, quietly enduring the Nord hostility that defines life in Windhelm for his people.",
        "display_name": "Aval Atheron - Gray Quarter Resident",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.5,
