        "content": "Faryl Atheron shares the Atheron family home in the Gray Quarter with his siblings Suvaris and Aval. Dunmer, keeps his head down and works where he can.",
        "display_name": "Faryl Atheron - Gray Quarter Resident",
        "emotion": "",
