        "content": "Bolfrida Brandy-Mug runs Brandy-Mug Farm outside Windhelm. Cheerful Nord woman, grows crops for the Candlehearth Hall and the city market.",
        "display_name": "Bolfrida Brandy-Mug - Farmer",
        "emotion": "",
